The State Journal-Register sports department publishes football statistics weekly throughout the high school season. Area statistics will appear online Monday night and in Tuesday's print edition. Submissions are due by 4 p.m. Mondays. Central State Eight statistics will appear online Tuesday night and in Wednesday's print edition. Submissions are due by 4 p.m. Tuesday. Coaches can submit their statistics by emailing sports@sj-r.com or calling (217) 788-1550. By The State Journal-Register
